code: public static void info(String message) {     System.out.println(message).     if (listener != null) {         listener.info(message).     } }
public static void infoPrint(String message) {     System.out.print(message).     if (listener != null) {         listener.infoPrint(message).     } }
public static void error(String message) {     System.err.println(message).     if (listener != null) {         listener.error(message).     } }
public static void error(Exception ex) {     ex.printStackTrace(System.err).     if (listener != null) {         listener.error(ex).     } }
static void setListener(LogListener listener) {     Log.listener = listener. }
